c: 8
v: 41
t: "Know that whatever spoils you take, one-fifth is for God and the Messenger, his close relatives, orphans, the poor, and ËąneedyËş travellers, if you ËątrulyËş believe in God and what We revealed to Our servant on that decisive day when the two armies met Ëąat BadrËş. And God is Most Capable of everything"